Benjamin Astbury was born 12 weeks early weighing just 1lb 3oz . 
  He suffered five cardiac arrests and was born with a bowel problem requiring two emergency operations . 
  He was put on a ventilator and given just a 10 per cent chance of survival . 
  But he is now thriving at home and is about to celebrate his first birthday . 
  His mother Taniya said 'miracles do happen'